Pre-conditions:
Project with test-case
Test was recorded on Window

Test steps:
1. Enter text in Script Viewer
2. Press "Ctrl+z" 
3. Make sure that change is canceled
4. Press "Ctrl+y"
5. Make sure that change is redo
6. Save all changes
7. Repeat steps 1-5 for context menu and main menu
